  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to assess the prevalence of overweight and obesity in 6 to 12
      year old children in Switzerland. This data will be used to investigate trends in the
      development of overweight and obesity in Switzerland. In addition, a questionnaire will be
      used to assess data on physical activity, nutrition, health and socioeconomic background and
      waist circumference as well as skin fold thicknesses will be measured.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
